channel.title: Rsps help (moparscape client)
channel.description: So I downloaded the moparscape client under the server downloads on the forums and I tried to log in using a random user/pass and the same message keeps popping up at the bottom in the text part saying "couldn't open output stream to log file." And then on the log in screen it says "No response from server. Please try using a different world". I'm new to this and could use all the help/assistance that I can get. Please help ASAP, Thank you!
